Y '''Omar Khayyám''', [[Persian language|Persian]] '''عمر خیام''' (mibait: [[Mayu 31]], [[1048]] king [[Nishapur]], [[Iran]] ([[Greater Iran|Persia]]) – mete: [[Disiembri 4]], [[1131]]), metung yang [[Persian people|Persian]] [[Persian literature|poeta]], matematiku at astronomer.

Dati yang mayayaus a ''Ghiyath al-Din Abu'l-Fath '''Omar''' ibn Ibrahim Al-Nisaburi '''Khayyámi''' ''(غیاث الدین ابو الفتح '''عمر''' بن ابراهیم '''خیام''' نیشابوری). Y Khayyám (خیام) metung  [[Arabic language|Arabic]] a meyandam a kataya ing kabaldugan na mangawang tent.<!-- Where did he die? And how? --> Bantug ya kareng inagap nang kawatasan a [[Rubaiyat nang Omar Khayyam]].

